ons%2C%20those%20goods%20likely%20came%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20imposed%20a%20broad%20145%25%20tariff%20on%20China%2C%20while%20some%20Chinese%20goods%20have%20been%20hit%20with%20even%20higher%20tariff%20rates.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-china-tariffs-fewer-dolls-us-children-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecabinet%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20White%20House%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20trade%20relations%20with%20China%2C%20Trump%20waved%20off%20concerns%20that%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-increase-prices-empty-shelves-timeline-supply-chain-holidays-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshelves%20would%20be%20empty%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20children%20will%20have%20two%20dolls%20instead%20of%2030%20dolls%2C%20and%20maybe%20the%20two%20dolls%20would%20cost%20a%20couple%20of%20bucks%20more%20than%20they%20would%20normally%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20imports%20about%2080%25%20of%20all%20its%20toys%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efrom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-speedy-tariffs-much-more-prepared-for-trump-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Toy%20Association.%20However%2C%20most%20Chinese%20goods%20would%20likely%20fall%20under%20the%20category%20of%20necessities%2C%20while%20others%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20American%20life%20that%20cannot%20easily%20be%20replaced%20with%20American-made%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20products%20that%20are%20subjected%20to%20tariffs%20were%20never%20made%20in%20the%20US%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20make%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Willy%20C.%20Shih%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20management%20practice%20in%20business%20administration%20at%20Harvard%