3EHospitals%20count%20on%20medical%20equipment%20from%20China%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Commerce%2C%2094%25%20of%20first-aid%20kits%20and%20boxes%20imported%20to%20the%20US%20came%20from%20China%2C%20as%20well%20as%2040%25%20of%20rubber%20medical%20gloves%20and%2054%25%20of%20all%20medical%20adhesive%20dressings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Biden%20administration%20announced%20a%20plan%20to%20raise%20tariffs%20on%20many%20China-made%20items%20in%20May%202024%2C%20the%20American%20Hospital%20Association%20published%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aha.org%2F2024-07-01-fact-sheet-impact-tariffs-health-care-equipment%23%3A~%3Atext%3DImports%2520of%2520syringes%252C%2520medical%2520masks%2Chikes%2520will%2520take%2520effect%2520vary.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efact%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20that%20any%20broad%20tariffs%20on%20China%20would%20impact%20the%20prices%20of%20basic%20medical%20equipment%20like%20syringes%2C%20medical%20masks%2C%20respirators%2C%20and%20gloves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20medical%20supply%20expenses%20account%20for%20only%20around%2010.5%25%20of%20an%20average%20hospital's%20budget%2C%20they%20collectively%20accounted%20for%20%24146.9%20billion%20in%202023%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20%246.6%20billion%20over%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20ended%20up%20extending%20exemptions%20to%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fus-lifts-tariffs-on-chinese-medical-supplies-amid-coronavirus-outbreak-2020-3-1028973176%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20May%2031%2C%202025%2C%20including%20single-use%20sterile%20drapes%2C%20laparotomy%20sponges%2C%20and%20anesthesia%20instruments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20these%20exemptions%20still%20hold%20under%20Trump's%20executive%20orders%20that%20did%20not%20specify%20exemptions%2C%20US%20Customs%20