r%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Vice%20President%20to%20building%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20vending%20machine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Janakpuri%2C%20West%20Delhi%2C%20Sagar%20always%20had%20an%20unshakable%20love%20for%20food%2C%20especially%20the%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20his%20hometown.%20%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20Delhi%2C%20%3Cem%3Echhole%20kulche%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20a%20staple.%20But%20when%20I%20lived%20in%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20could%20never%20find%20the%20same%20authentic%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remembers.%20The%20craving%20for%20that%20delicious%20and%20spicy%20%3Cem%3Echhole%3C%2Fem%3E%20never%20left%20him.%20He%20would%20often%20wonder%20why%20North%20India%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20food%20is%20not%20available%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20over%2014%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20prestigious%20banks%20like%20Citibank%20and%20Credit%20Suisse%2C%20steadily%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder.%20Even%20though%20he%20was%20fond%20of%20his%20full-time%20job%2C%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20shake%20off%20the%20idea%20of%20doing%20something%20of%20his%20own.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20during%20a%20senior%20management%20programme%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20in%202023%20that%20I%20met%20people%20who%20were%20doing%20things%20beyond%20their%20regular%20jobs%2C%20including%20CEOs%2C%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20bloggers.%20That%20made%20me%20realise%20that%20if%20they%20can%20do%20it%2C%20so%20can%20I%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cf