%E2%80%99t%20realise%20how%20being%20able%20to%20just%20open%20a%20book%20and%20skim%20through%20notes%20when%20we%20want%20to%20revise%20a%20topic%2C%20helps.%20Navigating%20a%20PDF%20is%20tough.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351050%2Fupsc-cse-how-to-make-notes-ips-officer-rishabh-bhola-shares-tips-tricks-techniques%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENote-making%20is%20such%20a%20crucial%20process%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20studying.%20But%2C%20sometimes%2C%20even%20AI%20is%20not%20able%20to%20decipher%20handwritten%20notes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20often%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20Manu%2C%20who%20missed%20being%20able%20to%20type%20things%20out%20while%20studying%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20never%20let%20it%20deter%20him%20from%20his%20goal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20UPSC%20is%20a%20rigorous%20process%20and%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20hard%20work%20to%20be%20put%20in.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20I%20had%20to%20put%20in%20that%20little%20extra%20to%20compensate%20for%20the%20disability.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManu%20came%20up%20with%20a%20hack.%20He%20memorised%20the%20QWERTY%20keyboard.%20%E2%80%9CI%20kept%20my%20fingers%20on%20the%20keys%20A%2C%20S%2C%20B%2C%20H%2C%20J%2C%20K%2C%20L%2C%20semicolon%20and%20learnt%20typing%20at%20the%20speed%20of%2026%20words%20per%20minute.%20This%20helped%20me%20take%20down%20notes%20on%20my%20mobile%20phone.%20It%20let%20me%20type%20even%20when%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20keyboard.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fupsc-cse-1746191683.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manu%20Garg%20is%20a%20visually%20impaired%20student%20who%20secured%20an%20AIR%2091%20in%20the%20UPSC%20CSE%202024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3