%20the%20United%20States%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20EV%20Doctor%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20simple%20device.%20But%20inside%20its%20300-gram%20frame%20lies%20a%20powerful%20system%20built%20around%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20years%20of%20battery-specific%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditional%20battery%20testing%20relies%20heavily%20on%20charge-discharge%20cyclers%2C%20or%20CDC%20machines%2C%20which%20are%20bulky%20systems%20that%20take%20seven%20to%20eight%20hours%20to%20provide%20basic%20statistics%20like%20voltage%20and%20capacity.%20These%20metrics%20alone%20are%20insufficient%20for%20diagnosing%20deeper%20battery%20issues%20such%20as%20internal%20resistance%20or%20early-stage%20safety%20faults%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Shubham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEV%20Doctor%20changed%20the%20game.%20Instead%20of%20taking%20hours%20to%20test%20a%20battery%20like%20traditional%20machines%2C%20it%20uses%20smart%20technology%20to%20check%20everything%20in%20just%2015%20minutes.%20It%20looks%20at%20how%20the%20battery%20behaves%20when%20electricity%20flows%20through%20it%20and%20uses%20over%2025%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F406804%2Fifs-varun-jain-ai-human-elephant-conflict-chhattisgarh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20its%20overall%20health%2C%20safety%2C%20performance%2C%20and%20faults.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20device%20works%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20batteries%2C%20whether%20they%20use%20advanced%20communication%20systems%20like%20Controller%20Area%20Network%20(CAN)%20or%20not%2C%20and%20can%20test%20batteries%20up%20to%20100%20volts%20and%20100%20ampere-hours%20in%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBattery%20tests%20that%20take%20minutes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20a%20user%20has%20to%20do%20is%20connect%20t