%20to%20operate%20and%20can%20be%20easily%20learned%20within%20a%20span%20of%20two%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Gokul%20Krishan%2C%20the%20Chief%20Technical%20Officer%20(CTO)%20at%20Altersage%20Innovations%2C%20who%20has%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20company%20for%20over%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAmong%20the%20elements%2C%20building%20the%20robotic%20arm%20took%20time%2C%20as%20it%20was%20challenging%20to%20replicate%20the%20hand%20movement%20of%20a%20human%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gokul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChanging%20the%20future%20of%20coconut%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoco-bot%20aims%20to%20revolutionise%20coconut%20farming%20by%20making%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F320826%2Fbengaluru-professor-saji-varghese-makes-sunbird-straws-from-coconut-leaves-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esafer%20and%20more%20accessible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CClimbing%20a%2020-metre%20tree%20is%20extremely%20risky%20and%20physically%20demanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ashin%2C%20who%20even%20attempted%20it%20himself%20at%20a%20workshop%20in%20Thrissur.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20easy%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20safety%20measures%20in%20place.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%E2%80%99s%20vision%20includes%20deploying%20Coco-bot%20at%20the%20district%20and%20%3Cem%3Epanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%20levels%2C%20empowering%20rural%20communities%2C%20particularly%20Kudumbashree%20women%20and%20ASHA%20workers%2C%20to%20earn%20a%20steady%20income%2C%20which%20is%20estimated%20at%20around%20Rs%2018%2C000%20to%20Rs%2020%2C000%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20through%20operating%20the%20bot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FM